org.xlattice.protocol.stun

Class BindingResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.xlattice.protocol.stun.StunMsg
      • org.xlattice.protocol.stun.BindingResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StunConst

    public class BindingResponse
extends StunMsg
    A BindingResponse must have MappedAddress, SourceAddress, and ChangedAddress attributes. It might have ReflectedFrom and MessageIntegrity attributes. It may NOT have ResponseAddress, ChangeRequest, UserName, Password, ErrorCode, or UnknownAttribute attributes.
    Author:
    Jim Dixon
